data.description: Welcome to your new home! Set in the highly sought-after Hampton Brook subdivision, you'll enjoy convenient access to I-75, Downtown Hampton, and the excitement of the Atlanta Motor Speedway. Step right in to discover an open and inviting living room that comes complete with a cozy fireplace, perfect for those relaxed evenings. Just off the living room, you'll find the chef's kitchen – the heart of the home where all the deliciousness happens. The layout flows effortlessly, making it a breeze to hang out and make memories with family and friends. This gem of a home boasts four spacious bedrooms and three bathrooms that are as functional as they are stylish. Each bedroom is generously sized and packed with unique features like tray ceilings and accent wood walls that give a touch of personality. The lower level has a separate entrance, with one bedroom and one bathroom, with the potential for a secondary unit! Don't miss out on this charming opportunity to make this your own!
